 "subscription.email.content" : "<p>Hi {NAME},</p><p>Thank you for subscribing to {BROWSER}! We hope that you’ll enjoy our fun child-friendly content.</p><p>If you have any questions or concerns about {BROWSER}, you can visit our contact our support team by opening a <a href='https://installchameleon.com/ticket/' target='_blank'>Support Ticket.</a></p><p>Thank you!</p><p>{BROWSER} Team</p>", 
 "donation.email.subject" : "Thank You for Donation to Zac Browser", 
 "donation.email.content" : "<p>Hi {NAME} Thank You!</p><p>On behalf of Zac Browser, I would like to thank you so much for your generous donation.</p><p>Zac Browser, the world’s leading browser for children with autism, aims to create a better world for children with autism.</p><p>Your donation will go directly towards the cause of your choice, thus strengthening the autism community for their safety and well-being.</p><p>Please stay tuned for our latest news to see how your contribution is making a difference!</p><p>Kind regards,</p><p>Zac Browser Team</p>", 
